/* Command List

[1/2/3] Select output channels
[y/u/i] Load R/G/B into selected channel
[h/j/k] Load H/S/B into selected channel
[r] Sort row
[R] Sort row (reverse)
[f] Sort full channel
[F] Sort full channel (reverse)
[`] Toggle color mode output (RGB<=>HSB)
[t] Threshold channel
[p] Posterize channel
[b] Blur channel
[n] Invert channel
[s] Saves the image

end */
